<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> | Discord 인증 시스템</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col transition-colors duration-300">

    <div class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex-grow">
        <header class="fixed-nav-header py-4 shadow-md">
            <div class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex justify-between items-center">
                <h1 class="text-xl font-bold discord-blue">Verita BOT</h1>
                <nav class="text-sm space-x-4">
                    <a href="/" class="<%= title.includes('환영합니다') ? 'nav-link-active' : 'nav-link-normal' %> hover:underline font-medium">시스템 소개</a>
                    <a href="/QnA" class="<%= title.includes('Q&A') ? 'nav-link-active' : 'nav-link-normal' %> hover:underline font-medium">자주 묻는 질문</a>
                    <a href="/tos" class="<%= title.includes('약관') ? 'nav-link-active' : 'nav-link-normal' %> hover:underline font-medium">이용 약관</a>
                    <a href="/privacy" class="<%= title.includes('개인정보') ? 'nav-link-active' : 'nav-link-normal' %> hover:underline font-medium">개인정보</a>
                    <a href="/dashboard/login" class="bg-discord-blue hover:bg-indigo-600 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded transition-colors ml-4 shadow-md">관리자 대시보드</a>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </header>

        <section class="py-16 text-center" style="padding-top: 5rem;">
            <h2 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
                서버를 안전하게, <span class="discord-blue">AI 인증</span> 시스템
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                <strong>다중 계정</strong> 및 <strong>악성 유저</strong>를 사전에 방지하여, 건강하고 공정한 Discord 커뮤니티를 만드세요.
            </p>
            <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
                <a href="/invite" class="bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg text-lg transition duration-200 shadow-xl">
                    🤖 봇 초대하기
                </a>
                
                <% if (title.includes('환영합니다')) { %>
                <a href="#features" class="bg-discord-blue hover:bg-indigo-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg text-lg transition duration-200 shadow-xl">
                    시스템 특징 알아보기
                </a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div id="features" class="main-container p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-xl shadow-2xl w-full text-left mb-8">
            <header class="mb-6 border-b pb-4">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold discord-blue"><%= title %></h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">시스템 소개와 작동 원리입니다.</p>
            </header>
            
            <% if (title.includes('환영합니다')) { %>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold discord-blue mb-6">시스템의 3가지 핵심 기능</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
                <div class="p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-center feature-card">
                    <span class="text-3xl discord-blue mb-3 block">🚫</span>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">다중 계정 방지</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">네이버 이메일 인증과 기기 지문(Fingerprint ID) 추적을 통해 동일인물의 부계정 생성을 원천적으로 차단합니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-center feature-card">
                    <span class="text-3xl discord-blue mb-3 block">🧠</span>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">AI 위험 분석</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Gemini AI가 계정 연령, 유사 이메일 패턴 등을 복합 분석하여 관리자가 놓치기 쉬운 잠재적 위험을 경고합니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-center feature-card">
                    <span class="text-3xl discord-blue mb-3 block">📊</span>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">통합 대시보드</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">인증 통계, 사용자 로그, 연관 계정 기록 등을 웹 대시보드에서 실시간으로 확인하고 관리합니다.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <% } %>

            <div class="markdown-content"><%- contentHtml %></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-8 py-6 main-container-footer shadow-inner w-full">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-sm text-center footer-text">
            이 페이지는 디스코드 서버 인증 시스템의 일부입니다. | &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Verita BOT.
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
